    • Method Detail

      • deterministic

        default boolean deterministic()
        Determines if the fitness function is deterministic or not, i.e., if the value of the function for a given value can change in time (non-stationary) or not (stationary)
        Returns:
        true if the fitness function does not changes with time, false otherwise
